<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.10">
<l>kaṇṭār paḻiyāmē yakkākkāy kārvaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>vaṇṭār kuḻalvāra vāveṉṟa vāyccicol</l>
<l>viṇtōy matiḷvilli puttūrkkōṉ paṭṭaṉcol</l>
<l>koṇṭāṭip pāṭak kuṟukā viṉaitāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who praise the words of the scholar-king of Villiputtūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">with walls that touch the heavens,</l>
<l>[about] the words of the herdess who cried</l>
<l>“Caw! Caw! Come! Comb the curly hair</l>
<l rend="indent">full of bees of him with the dark complexion”</l>
<l rend="indent">[so that] those who see [him] wouldn’t ridicule [him]</l>
<l>[grasping this] poem, they will not attain [bad] karma.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
